[0.000, "o", "  \u001b[2mGPU availability varies by region and changes constantly.\u001b(B\u001b[m\r\n  \u001b[2mGCO checks Spot Placement Scores and instance availability\u001b(B\u001b[m\r\n  \u001b[2macross all configured regions to find where GPUs are right now.\u001b(B\u001b[m\r\n\r\n"]
