[0.000, "o", "  \u001b[2mKueue is the Kubernetes-native job queueing system.\u001b(B\u001b[m\r\n"]
[0.000, "o", "  \u001b[2mIt manages resource quotas, fair-sharing between teams, and\u001b(B\u001b[m\r\n  \u001b[2mholds jobs in a queue until cluster resources are available.\u001b(B\u001b[m\r\n"]
[0.000, "o", "  \u001b[2mThink of it as a resource-aware admission controller for batch jobs.\u001b(B\u001b[m\r\n\r\n"]
